        "conditions": "Approximately one-third of sequential revenue increase (~$33M at midpoint) is pricing; excluding pricing, organic sequential growth is approximately 7% vs stated 11%; channel repricing effective start of Q2; roughly half of price impact relates to channel inventory repricing that will not repeat in Q3",
